description:
If you think you live in a high-pressure environment, if you think you have to try to succeed in a hostile, very secular world, then you will want to get to know Daniel. In this program Gary Kent tells the story of a man who rose to incredible heights -- in an alien land. Don't miss the program and invite your friends to watch it too.

BIBLE CHARACTERS SERIES:
1. Daniel (Real Life Superhero): https://youtu.be/0PwGagJvWjg
2. Mary of Magdala: https://youtu.be/a-Zw917b-KY
3. James and John (The Suns of Thunder): https://youtu.be/Kb_Wwrdoiyo
4. Nicodemus (The Night Visitor): https://youtu.be/z7jsyleIiFU
5. Peter (The Fisherman): https://youtu.be/4nK8iNrx1qU
